docs.lead_paragraph: Joseph R. Biden Jr. began his 2020 campaign on Thursday, casting it as a rescue mission for a country facing a dire threat from its elected leader, President Trump. His announcement video was a three-and-a-half minute statement of political values, and an attempt to address why a 76-year-old former vice president is now returning to the campaign trail.

headline.main: Joe Biden’s Campaign Announcement Video, Annotated
